level system with scoreboard popping up at end of level
documentation of copyrighted material, libraries
post on github and write readme

Enemies keep spawning until you get enough coins.
If you get hit 3 times, you die and restart at level 1.
Skeletons give 2 coins
Ghosts give 1 coin

Ghost - 2 hits to kill
Skeleton - 3 hits to kill


resources:
https://ansimuz.itch.io/grotto-escape-chibi-monsters - Player and Monsters
https://savvycow.itch.io/perfectpixelfruit - Level Objects
https://ansimuz.itch.io/parallax-forest - Background
https://www.raylib.com/ - Engine